title: Kate Moss living with new beau?
text: 'Goosebumps' beats 'The Martian' to top US box office Monday, 19 October 2015 (14 minutes ago) Los Angeles, Oct 19 : Sony's "Goosebumps" beat " The Martian " to win the box office race this week, taking in $23.5 million in its opening weekend from across 3,501 theatres in North America. “Goosebumps” takes the No. 1 spot this weekend, bringing in an estimated $23.5 million and satisfying all your nostalgia needs.
